<view class="container safe"><view class="title">NFC 快速取件</view><view class="card"><view class="section-title">读取智能标签</view><view class="subtitle">靠近智能寻物标签，或在 NFC 不可用时手动输入标签内容。</view><button class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="read">读取 NFC 标签</button><textarea class="input" placeholder="手动输入标签内容" bindinput="input" value="{{raw}}"></textarea><view class="notice">{{tagText}}</view></view><view class="action-list"><button class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="confirmServer">确认快速取件</button><button class="btn btn-ghost" bindtap="confirmGateway">使用本地网关确认</button></view><view class="success" wx:if="{{resultText}}">{{resultText}}</view></view>
